ttps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fdsc-2257_orig.jpg&h=cfd4cef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">ABU SIMBEL 往ASWAN 的中途休息站</div><br />\n<br />\n廢話無多，介紹下個行程先。<br />\n<br />\nDay 0<br />\n香港至阿布扎比轉機，然後零晨2點零到開羅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6907_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6907_orig.jpg&h=7b74b6d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">從飛機上望落去埃及</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n早 : 埃及博物館<br />\n午 : 開羅伊斯蘭老城<br />\n晚 : 尼羅河<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/dsc-1896_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fdsc-1896_orig.jpg&h=76704fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">被聯合國教科文組織遺產保護的開羅伊斯蘭老城</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n早 : 直飛ABU SIMBEL<br />\n午 : ABU SIMBEL TEMPLE<br />\n晚 : ABU SIMBEL TEMPLE LIGHT SHOW<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-7232_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-7232_orig.jpg&h=6aa61770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Temples of Abu Simbel</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n早 : TEMPLE of ABU SIMBEL  日出，然後坐車到ASWAN，<br />\n午 : 參觀TEMPLE OF PHILAE，然後參觀阿努比人村落<br />\n晚 : 參觀香水店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/dsc-2285_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fdsc-2285_orig.jpg&h=18720be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">TEMPLE OF PHILAE</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n早 : 參觀Temple of Kom Ombo<br />\n午 : 參觀Temple of Horus<br />\n晚 : 乘郵輪往Luxor<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/dsc-2527_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fdsc-2527_orig.jpg&h=31186b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">參觀Temple of Horus<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n早 : 熱氣球，King valley，Temple of Hatshepsut, Temple of Amenhotep3 (Colossi of Memnon)<br />\n午 : 金字塔及獅身人面像<br />\n晚 : 沙漠騎馬狂奔，金字塔燈光SHOW<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/dsc-2724_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fdsc-2724_orig.jpg&h=2454b671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LUXOR 熱氣球</div><br />\n<br />\n咁中間既日子我就去左埃塞俄比亞&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-7621_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-7621_orig.jpg&h=c01fffab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">埃塞俄比亞既小學雞</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 15<br />\n早: 開羅市中心亂行去搵巴士站<br />\n午: 坐火車去阿歷山大港<br />\n晚: 坐錯火車，坐左架平民火車番開羅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-8100_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-8100_orig.jpg&h=e90c8aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">阿歷山大港火車</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 16<br />\n早: 飛到沙姆沙伊赫國際機場，然後坐車到DAHAB<br />\n午: 潛水<br />\n晚: 行西乃山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-8149_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-8149_orig.jpg&h=77350f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">DAHAB 的海邊午餐</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 17<br />\n早: 西乃山睇日出<br />\n午: DAHAB 市內遊走<br />\n晚: 飛回開羅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-8176_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-8176_orig.jpg&h=2c24ffbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">西乃山山頂同貓貓睇日出</div><br />\n<br />\nDay 18<br />\n早: 買手信<br />\n午: 坐飛機番香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-8214_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-8214_orig.jpg&h=a5c76b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃及行程洗費就之後再UPDATE(有MARK 但未入EXCEL 計)"},{"pid":"dd2c689fb88281128e6dd88b7080738325d5aabe","tid":107665,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"咁開始我地既埃及之旅之前都講小小埃及既背景先，等大家對呢個國家有少少認識先。(有D參考維基，如果有錯煩請大家更正，另外以下圖片均從GOOGLE搜尋回來。)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/flag-of-egypt-svg_orig.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fflag-of-egypt-svg_orig.png&h=d5ba008c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">埃及國旗</div><br />\n<br />\n歷史簡介<br />\n埃及，四大文明古國之一，其歷史可追朔至五千年前。<br />\n <br />\n前王朝時期<br />\n大約在公元前3300年，尼羅河民眾逐漸聚居，並形成原始的城邦<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/1_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2F1_orig.jpg&h=20f8a7c2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有關當時的埃及壁畫</div><br />\n<br />\n​早王朝時期<br />\n到公元前3100年，依傳說，曼尼斯創了第一王朝，統一南北埃及。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/early-dynastic-period-narmer_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fearly-dynastic-period-narmer_orig.jpg&h=794d48c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">其中一幅有關當時曼尼斯統一南北的藝術作品</div><br />\n<br />\n古王國時期<br />\n由公元前2685年開始，直到2200年完結。古埃及人在這段時期間興建大量金字塔及巨像，第五王朝開始拜太陽神，然後法老權力開始減弱，貴族權力上升，紛紛獨立，自立為王，步入第一中間期。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/step-pyramid-of-djoser_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fstep-pyramid-of-djoser_orig.jpg&h=6f6e10aa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">埃及史上第一座金字塔: 在古王國時期興建的階梯金字塔</div><br />\n<br />\n第一中間期<br />\n公元前2200年至公元前2050年，古埃及王國南北分裂，戰爭不斷，最後由埃及中部底比斯政權統一埃及，進入繁榮的新時期，中王國時期。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/hb-13-182-3_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fhb-13-182-3_orig.jpg&h=4ca5df5e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有關當時的法老向太陽神及月亮神奉獻的石碑</div><br />\n<br />\n中王國時期<br />\n公元前2050年至公元前1750年，由於步入繁榮富裕，文化交流加速，金字塔等大型建築不斷興造。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/published/300px-kneelingstatueofsobekhotepv-altesmuseum-berlin.png?1486884012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fpublished%2F300px-kneelingstatueofsobekhotepv-altesmuseum-berlin.png%3F1486884012&h=d62559fc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">其中一個當時的法老: Merhotepre Sobekhotep<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n第二中間期<br />\n始於前十七世紀，由於敘利亞的希克索斯人駕著當時埃及人未見過的戰車及戰爭技術入侵，然後就步入了外族統治的第二中間期。直到大約公元前1550年，亞摩斯崛起，趕走外族，進入新王國時期。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/beni-hassan-lepsius-bh-3-03_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fbeni-hassan-lepsius-bh-3-03_orig.jpg&h=2b0bccac&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有關希克索斯人入侵埃及後的壁畫</div><br />\n<br />\n新王國時期<br />\n約公元前1550年至公元前1076年，途中不斷征戰，其勢力更擴張到敘利亞及尼羅河第四瀑布，橫跨北非和西亞。底比斯政權如日中天，但由於祭司權力過度傾斜，祭司謀朝篡位，步入最黑暗的第三中間期。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/published/2007-3-31-picture2-ss.jpg?1486885217\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fpublished%2F2007-3-31-picture2-ss.jpg%3F1486885217&h=d10d69db&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">其中一個當時的皇后雕像</div><br />\n<br />\n第三中間期<br />\n由公元前1076年開始至公元前702年。埃及內部分裂，中間經歷了利比亞部族及蘇丹北部部族統治。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/published/herihor-papyrus-2-med-hr.png?1486885910\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fpublished%2Fherihor-papyrus-2-med-hr.png%3F1486885910&h=a0d61e29&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">在當時有重大權力的祭司</div><br />\n<br />\n後王朝時期<br />\n公元前712年開始，接二連三受到其他外族侵略，又被亞述人重創埃及，但隨後普薩美提克一世重新統一埃及，驅逐亞述人，再現繁榮盛世。但隨後波斯帝國崛起，入侵及統治埃及，直至公元前332年，馬其頓國王亞歷山大大帝揮軍結束古埃及王國。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/hb-2003-154_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fhb-2003-154_orig.jpg&h=ecf5bafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">當時的木雕</div><br />\n<br />\n在古埃及帝國完結後，埃及曾受到希臘、羅馬、阿拉伯、奧斯曼等帝國統治，其後又成為法國及英國的屬地，並於1922年脫離英國獨立，埃及王國成立<br />\n<br />\n埃及現代史<br />\n直到1952年爆發7月革命，埃及共和國成立，並由軍方接管。直到2011年，阿拉伯之春由突尼西亞爆發，穆巴拉克下台，並舉行第一次總統民選，由穆爾西當選，但隨後經濟進一步惡化，其政令又加劇國內矛盾，令政局更為不穩。隨後穆爾西遭到軍方罷黜，並委任阿德里&middot;曼蘇爾擔任臨時總統，最後軍方提前大選，結果由阿卜杜勒成為最新一任總統。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/egypt1_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fegypt1_orig.jpg&h=b0949d30&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">阿拉伯之春在埃及所引起的示威</div>"},{"pid":"a6cdf17f3519ff8f65a4e6fff9863269b51ebaed","tid":107665,"uid":6477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"宗教<br />\n在公元400年至800年，基督教曾是大多埃及人的信仰。其後由於曾經受到阿拉伯帝國的統治，伊斯蘭教自始成為國教，並成為大多埃及人的宗教信仰(大約90%)。而現在只有10%的人口信仰為基督教。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/51176582-011201654-1_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2F51176582-011201654-1_orig.jpg&h=d6c1b059&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">當地基督教徒與穆斯林一起參與示威</div><br />\n<br />\n地理<br />\n疆域呈不規則四方型，有95%為沙漠，其國境可分與利比亞為鄰的西部沙漠區，尼羅河流域，東臨紅海並與巴勒斯坦、以色列接壤的西奈半島，及東部沙漠區。其最高峰凱瑟琳山為於西奈半島，海拔2,629米。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/20151019061038-36130_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2F20151019061038-36130_orig.jpg&h=f13dc99f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">埃及地勢圖</div><br />\n<br />\n行政<br />\n自阿拉伯之春開始，埃及是軍事管制下的共和國。立法權歸屬政府和埃及議會，而現有政黨及政治組織近百個。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/mbs_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fmbs_orig.jpg&h=4c9ced66&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">曾經的政黨:穆斯林兄弟會</div><br />\n<br />\n經濟與消費水平<br />\n埃及經濟主要依賴於農業、石油出口、旅遊業，以及勞務出口。而消費水平也相當便宜，開羅面包店買一個面包大約港幣2元。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/873482471_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2F873482471_orig.jpg&h=31163982&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">埃及最出名的農產品 : 棉</div><br />\n<br />\n天氣<br />\n最好於十月到二月時旅遊，夏天會非常熱，而且日夜溫差大，而一月份最冷(我有女仔FRIEND 十二月尾去埃及，佢都要著好幾件HEAT TEC 加羽絨)，我就冇著HEAT TEC 加羽絨，夜晚或者朝早係開羅真係會凍死人。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/published/1743137661.png?1486889385\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fpublished%2F1743137661.png%3F1486889385&h=747d2181&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">開羅天氣圖</div><br />\n<br />\n貨幣與匯率<br />\n通用貨幣為埃磅，係旅遊區美金都可以用到，而且仲會抵過用埃磅。<br />\n我去個時兌1美金兌17.4埃磅，當我十日後再返去時就升到1美元兌18埃磅，而家就一美元兌18.7埃磅，即係1 EGP (埃磅)等於0.41 HKD (港幣)。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/miro-egyptian-pounds-sukuk_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fmiro-egyptian-pounds-sukuk_orig.jpg&h=154361fa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">埃及貨幣 : 埃磅</div><br />\n<br />\n行前準備<br />\n老實講，出發前都冇咩點準備過，所以一開始係埃及自由行係勁慘，洗多左好多錢。而且點都好，一定要買LONELY PLANET，會方便搵野食同搵路好多。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/51wpn4i758l-sx323-bo1-204-203-200_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2F51wpn4i758l-sx323-bo1-204-203-200_orig.jpg&h=631783e4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">去之前一定要睇 既LONELY PLANET</div><br />\n<br />\n簽証<br />\n香港人持特區護照免簽証<br />\n<br />\n​序章完"},{"pid":"e44834cb40ba452db683f80d93dce731dc3e2eeb","tid":107665,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"留名睇遊記<br />\n<br />\n網上識個埃及fd話依家埃及銀紙跌得好甘<br />\n2010年1蚊美金兌7蚊埃及錢<br />\n今年就1兌20"},{"pid":"5f15a584b346b1c885c26df01aa17f782ca5b514","tid":107665,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇遊記<br />\n<br />\n網上識個埃及fd話依家埃及銀紙跌得好甘<br />\n2010年1蚊美金兌7蚊埃及錢<br />\n今年就1兌20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，應該仲會再跌落去，所以d 人勁鐘意收美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1ad5937041f6c049f67e796c44ee611504e506","tid":107665,"uid":4184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名睇遊記<br />\n<br />\n網上識個埃及fd話依家埃及銀紙跌得好甘<br />\n2010年1蚊美金兌7蚊埃及錢<br />\n今年就1兌20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，應該仲會再跌落去，所以d 人勁鐘意收美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直收美金令埃及錢需求減少，又會一直跌，惡性循環嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045dbce1c50da29128d40ab9ceebca11ce7f1d28","tid":107665,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">DAY 0</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6916_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6916_orig.jpg&h=3bed8e24&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">PHOTO OF THE DAY : 開羅上空</div><br />\n<br />\n仲記得個日明明夜晚6點就飛，但因為前幾日掛住搞畢業D野，都冇時間去買要用既野(仲要晏就先訂好晒D酒店既野)，搞到個日3點幾先臨急臨忙飛的趕去機場，不過去到機場CHECK IN時先發覺仲有個零鐘先飛，即刻係書局是但買左本埃及既旅遊書來係機上惡補埃及既野(所以我真係做左好少準備)，然後又影埋之後去埃塞做落地VISA 用既相就9沖入閘，然後食埋香港既最後一餐，是但影一張閘口相就上左呢班阿提哈德既航班，向轉機點，阿布札比出發。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6887_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6887_orig.jpg&h=f1d67309&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">往阿布札比去!!</div><br />\n<br />\n上到機時，好多人都打橫咁訓左係到，唉，鬼叫自己遲上機，唯有當吸收經驗，下次早D排隊上機啦，而坐係我隔離，就係一個來自COSTARICA ，識講廣東話既華人。雖然佢好煩，成日問東問西，但係機上佢都好照顧我，流鼻血個時都好TAKE CARE我。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6889_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6889_orig.jpg&h=0b307fb9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">SLEEPING PACK~</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6890_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6890_orig.jpg&h=11aa9427&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有自殺特攻隊睇！！</div><br />\n<br />\nBTW，阿提哈德雖然我就覺得唔太好坐，飛機餐都麻麻，上網又要收錢，不過佢做PROMOTION 咁平，所以其實都還可以既。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6898_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6898_orig.jpg&h=4ba9474a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">仲有N年前既愛回家睇</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6907_1_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6907_1_orig.jpg&h=1b082dd5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">阿布札比夜景</div><br />\n<br />\n到左阿布札比後，我只有1個鐘轉機時間，落到機就二話不說就趕去轉機閘口，然後就坐細機飛去開羅啦<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6916_1_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6916_1_orig.jpg&h=0c9b67ac&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">開羅夜景</div><br />\n<br />\n到步之後，已經零晨2點半，去到開羅機場，俾我想像中簡單，然後就即刻睇下機場兌換店既匯率，點知3間都唔同(之前係其他地方見到間間都一樣)，咁我就係最高匯率兌換店換住少少先，就去排隊等入境啦，btw，排隊過關時還可以，點知一去到行李安檢，個到d人就打晒尖咁，然後又見到幾個埃及人係到好大聲咁嘈交，差d開片咁，天啊，唔通呢個就係我一直其待既埃及？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6920_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6920_orig.jpg&h=e7697422&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">終於到開羅機場啦！</div><br />\n<br />\n出到去之後，當然少不免一堆埃及人沖上來，係咁問taxi taxi？不過我就都叫有d旅行經驗，都知呢d一定會俾人當做水魚，所以之前已經SEND埋EMAIL去HOSTEL叫人開車黎接我(咁夜坐的士一定會做水魚)，所以就一直係咁nonono，然後見到我個名，就跟住個個人坐佢架車返hostel，而係車途上我係咁問佢埃及既安全問題，佢都好強調而家既埃及係好安全，仲話好多都係遙言黎，而更多既時侯，係其他中東國家中傷佢地，的確，如果對中東國家有d認識，都會知埃及同其他中東國家既關係都係麻麻地。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6921_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6921_orig.jpg&h=3affada7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6922_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6922_orig.jpg&h=8735c169&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">本日入住旅店</div><br />\n<br />\nBtw，去到hostel，wow，估唔到咁舊咁正，咁有個種埃及古城feel，而架lift仲要勁古老咁。上到去，放好晒d野入房之後，負責人就叫左我去一邊坐，話想同我傾下個行程，呢個時侯心諗，成廿幾個鐘冇咩點訓過，俾我訓啦好嗎&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n而當然，佢唔係單單就咁幫我睇行程咁簡單啦，佢其實係想捉我報一d當地團(我估應該有佣金收)，而我當時廿幾個鍾冇訓，最後都係頂唔順佢既攻勢，報左一個當地尼羅河路線團加金字塔團(佢個時話300蚊美金全包，no tipping，係買野錢先要自己俾(而最後結果當然唔係咁啦)，就係咁，我係埃及既獨遊自由行之旅就冇左一半，而另一半就好在我同佢講話等我去完埃塞番黎先諗，唔係我個trip 真係會少好多experience。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6925_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6925_orig.jpg&h=fa46c731&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mrheykay.weebly.com/uploads/8/4/7/7/84779162/img-6925_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrheykay.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F8%2F4%2F7%2F7%2F84779162%2Fimg-6925_orig.jpg&h=fa46c731&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">旅店房間內部</div><br />\n<br />\nbtw交埋錢之後，問佢可唔可以第二朝帶我去買sim卡上網，佢話第二朝個staff會幫我搞，講埋第二朝早餐後，我就即刻番床訓，然後望一望個鐘，差唔多6點，即係按原本我安排既行程，仲有個零鐘就要出門口啦&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n呢鋪gg了。<br />\n <br />\nDay 0 完"},{"pid":"06a85f985710e735702a5c8f03fa877f8f233e14","tid":107665,"uid":6477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名睇遊記<br />\n<br />\n網上識個埃及fd話依家埃及銀紙跌得好甘<br />\n2010年1蚊美金兌7蚊埃及錢<br />\n今年就1兌20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，應該仲會再跌落去，所以d 人勁鐘意收美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直收美金令埃及錢需求減少，又會一直跌，惡性循環嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈哈，但早幾日check 又升番去之前個水平"},{"pid":"f154c7c2d191a1029ff4402dd9186d9591fd60db","tid":107665,"uid":18815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"喂！文呢<br />\n我下個月去呀"}]}